hadiths[60]{hadithnumber,text}:
4291,"Janab Abu-Alqama ne kaha ke merey ilm aur yaqeen ke mutabiq Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kiya hai, aapney farmaya : '' beshak Jalal Wala Allah har sau saal ke shuru mein ya aakhir mein is ummat ke andar eik aadmi paida karta rahega jo uskey deen ko naye sire se nau-qaaim aur mazboot karta rahega. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke is riwayat ko Abdur-Rehman bin Shureh Skandaraani ne (معضل) bayan kiya hai, wo Sharaaheel se aagey nahin badha . (is ne baad waley raawiyon ka zikr chhod diya hai.)"
4292,"Hassaan bin Atiya kehtey hain ke Mak-hool aur ibne Abu-Zakariya, Khalid bin Maadaan ki taraf rawana huey aur main bhi unke sath chal diya. to Khalid ne Jubair bin Nafair se eik hadees riwayat ki jo (هدنة) (musaalihat (samjhauta)) ke mutalliq thi. phir Jubair ne kaha : chalen Hazrat Zi-Mukhbir (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan chaltey hain jo ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke Sahaba mein se they. ham unke paas pahunchey to Jubair ne un se (هدنة) (musaalihat) ke mutalliq puchha . to unhoney kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna hai : ''tum log roomiyon se eik pur-amn musaalihat karogey. aur phir unke sath mil kar apney peechhey eik dushman se jang karogey, un par ghalib rahogey , ghanimat pao gey aur sahih salaamat rahogey, phir wahan se wapis lauto-gey aur eik maidan mein utro gey jis mein tiley bhi hongey . to esaiyon mein se eik aadmi saleeb buland kerega aur kahega : saleeb ghalib aa gaee . to musalmanon mein se eik aadmi ko ghussa aaeyga aur wo usey qatl kar daley ga . to us mauqe par Romi dhoka karengey aur jang ke liye jama ho jaeyngey.''"
4293,"Hassaan bin Atiya ne ye hadees bayan ki aur mazeed kaha : ''musalman jaldi se apney aslahey ki taraf uthen gey aur un se qitaal karengey aur Allah unhen shahadat se sarfaraaz farmaeyga. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : is sanad mein Waleed ne ba-waaste Jubair, Hazrat Zi-Mukhbir (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kiya hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke Rooh, Yahya bin Hamza aur Bishr bin Bakr ne Auzaai se riwayat kiya jaisey ke Esa ne kaha."
4294,"Hazrat Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''baitul-Maqdis ki abadi yasrab (Madiney) ki be-abadi ka pesh khema hogi. aur yasrab ki be-abadi ke natijey mein badi jang hogi aur us jang ka zuhoor Qustuntuniya ki Fateh hoga. aur Qustuntuniya ki Fateh ke baad dajjaal aaeyga.'' phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apna haath is hadees ke bayan kerney waley (Hazrat Muaz (Raziallahu anhu)) ki raan ya kandhey par maara, phir farmaya : ''bila-shuba ye waqia is tarah haq hai jaisey ke tum yahan ho ya baithey huey ho.'' murad Hazrat Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) they."
4295,"Hazrat Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jange-azeem, Fateh Qustuntuniya aur dajjaal ki aamad saat mahinon mein hogi.''"
4296,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Basar (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jange-azeem aur shehar (qustuntuniya) ki Fateh chhe saal ke arsay mein hogi aur maseeh dajjaal ka nikalna saatwen mein hoga. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke ye riwayat Esa ki (mazkura baala) riwayat se sahih tar hai."
4297,"Hazrat Soban (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aisa waqt aaney wala hai ke dusri ummaten tumharey khilaf eik doosrey ko bulaeyngi jaisey ke khaney waley apney piyaley par eik doosrey ko bulatey hain.'' to kehney waley ne kaha : kya ye hamari un dino qillat aur kami ki wajeh se hoga? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''(nahin) balke tum un dino bahut ziyada hogey, lekin jhaag hogey jis tarah ke sailab ka jhaag hota hai. Allah taala tumharey dushman ke seenon se tumhari heybiyat nikal dega aur tumharey dilon mein (''وهن'') dal dega.'' poochhney waley ne puchha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! (وهن) se kya murad hai? aapney farmaya : ''duniya ki mohabbat aur maut ki karaahat.''"
4298,"Hazrat Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jang ke moqe par musalmanon ka khema (markaz) dimashq naami shehar ki janib mein waqey maqamre-ghota hoga aur Dimashq Shaam ke behtareen shehron mein se hoga.''"
4299,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''an-qareeb musalman Madiney mein gher liye jaeyngey yahan tak ke unki baeed (door) tareen chhaawni us waqt salaah maqam par hogi .''"
4300,Janab Zohri (Rahimahullah) se marwi (bayan) hai ke salaah ka maqam khaibar ke qarib hai.
4301,Yahya bin Jabir Taai (Rahimahullah) se riwayat hai jabke Harun bin Abdullah ki sanad mein . . . Yahya Hazrat Auf bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah taala is ummat mein do talwaarein hergiz jama nahin farmaeyga ke eik talwaar inke aapas mein chaley aur dusri unka dushman chalaey.
4302,"Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke eik sahabi se riwayat hai, wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bayan kartey hain ke aapney farmaya : ''habshiyon se ta'ruz (chhed-chhad) na karo jab tak ke wo tumharey dar pai na hon aur turkon ko bhi chhodey raho jab tak ke wo tumhen chhodey rahen.''"
4303,"Saiyedna Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''qiyamat us waqt tak nahin aaeygi jab tak ke musalmanon ki turkon se jang na ho jaey. ye aisey log hongey ke unke chehrey dhaalon ki manind hongey, jin par chamdaa waghaira lagaya gaya ho. aur unka libas baalon ka hoga.''"
4304,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''qiyamat us waqt tak nahin aaeygi jab tak ke tum (musalman) eik qom se jang na kar lo jinkey jootey baalon ke hongey. aur us waqt tak qiyamat nahin aaeygi jab tak ke tum eik qom se jang na kar lo jin ki aankhen chhoti aur naakhein chapti hongi , unke chehrey goya dhaale hongi jin par chamdaa waghaira laga hota hai.''"
4305,"Janab Abdullah bin Barida apney walid se bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apni eik hadees mein farmaya : ''eik qom tum se jang karegi jin ki aankhen chhoti chhoti hongi yani turk. farmaya : tum unhen teen baar dhakelo-gey yahan tak ke jazeera arab ke kinarey par pahuncha dogey. pehli dafa dhakelne mein un mein se jo bhag jaeyngey najat pa jaeyngey, dusri dafa mein kuchh bach jaeyngey aur kuchh halak hongey. lekin teesri baar mein unka safaayaa kar diya jaeyga.'' ya usi ki manind bayan farmaya."
4306,"Janab Muslim bin Abu-Bakra kehtey hain ke maine apney walid se suna, bayan kartey they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''meri ummat ke kuchh log nichey ke ilaqey ki zameen mein utren gey jisey Basra kehtey hongey jo dariyaaey-dajla ke kinarey abad hoga aur us par eik pul hoga. uski abadi bahut ziyada hogi aur ye muhaajiron ka shehar hoga. ibne Yahya ne bayan kiya ke Abu-Ma'mar ne kaha : ''ye musalmanon ka shehar hoga , isliye jab aakhiri zamana hoga to bano qantoora (turk, ye unke bade buzurg ka naam hai) aaeyngey, unke chehrey chaudey aur aankhen chhoti-chhoti hongi yahan tak ke wo is dariya ke kinarey utren-gey to is shehar ke log teen jamaaton mein bat jaeyngey : eik jamaat bailon ki dumen pakad leygi aur jangalon mein nikal jaeygi aur is tarah wo halak hongey. dusri jamaat apney liye aman talab karegi aur wo kafir ho jaeyngey . aur teesri jamaat wo hogi jo apni aulad (ki parwa na kartey huey unhen) apni peeth peechhey chhod kar unke sath qitaal karegi aur yehi log azeem shuhda hongey.''"
4307,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne un se farmaya tha : ''aey Anas ! log kaee shehar aabad karengey, un mein se eik shehar ka naam Basra ya baseera hoga, agar tum uskey paas se guzro ya us mein dakhil ho to wahan ki sabaakh (colour-zada zameen) aur ''کلاء'' maqam se door rehna, uskey bazaron aur uskey ameeron ke darwazon se bhi bachna, uskey aas-paas rahne ko ikhtiyar karna. bila-shuba us zameen mein (khasaf) (dhans jana), pattharon ki barish aur zalzale hongey. aur aisey log bhi hongey jo (Shaam ko sahih salaamat hongey magar) subah karengey to bandar aur suwar bin chukey hongey.''"
4308,"Ibrahim bin Saleh bin Dirham kehtey hain ke maine apney walid se suna, wo kehtey they ke ham log hajj ke liye rawana huey to ittifaq se ham se eik aadmi ne puchha : tumharey qarib pehlu mein abla naami koi basti hai? ham ne kaha : haan, to usney kaha : tum mein se kon mera zaamin banta hai ke wo merey liye masjid ishaar mein do ya chaar rakatein padhey aur kahie ke ye Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ke liye hain? maine apney khaleel Abul-Qaasim (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna hai : ''Shan Wale Allah qiyamat ke din masjid ishaar se shahidon ko uthaeyga. shohdaaey Badr ke sath un logon ke alawa aur koi nahin utheyga. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke ye masjid darya ke kinarey par hai."
4309,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''(kuffar) habsha jab tak tum se ta'ruz (chhed-chhaad) na keren tum bhi unhen chhodey raho. bila-shuba kaabey ka khazana nikalney wala eik Habshi hi hoga jiski pindliyan chhoti-chhoti hongi.''"
4310,"Janab Abu-Zara'a (Rahimahullah) ne bataya ke eik jamaat Madina Munawwara mein Marwan (bin Hakam) ke yahan gaee. unhoney us se alaamaate qiyamat ke silsiley mein suna ke sab se pehley dajjaal nikley ga. kehtey hain, phir main Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu Anhuma) ke yahan hazir hua aur unhen ye bataya to Abdullah ne kaha : usney tumhen kuchh nahin bataya. maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna hai aap farmatey they : ''beshak un alaamaat mein sab se pehley ye hai ke Suraj maghrib ki taraf se tulu hoga ya chaasht ke waqt ''janwar'' zahir hoga, jo bhi pehley hua doosra uskey baad ho jaeyga. Hazrat Abdullah ne kaha : aur qadim (puraani) kitaben unke zere-mutaalia rehti thin. mera khayal hai ke un mein se pehli alamat Suraj ka maghrib ki janib se tulu hona hai."
4311,"Hazrat Huzefa bin Usaid Ghifaari (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, wo kehtey hain ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke kamrey ke saye mein baithey baaten kar rahey they ke ham ne qiyamat ka zikr kiya aur hamari aawazen buland huin to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''qiyamat us waqt tak hergiz nahin aaeygi jab tak ke us se pehley das nishaniyan zahir na hon. Suraj ka maghrib ki janib se tulu hona, janwar ka nikalna, yajooj Majuj ka zuhoor, dajjaal ka khurooj (bagawat), Esa ibne Maryam Alehissalam ki aamad , dakhan yani dhuwan, teen janib mein zameen ka dhansaayaa jana : eik maghrib mein, doosra mashriq mein aur teesra jazeera arab mein aur unke aakhir mein Yamen se yani beech adn se aag nikleygi jo logon ko mehshar mein chala ley jaeygi (ilaaqa shaam mein jama kar degi).''"
4312,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''qiyamat us waqt tak qaaim nahin hogi jab tak ke Suraj apni maghrib ki janib se tulu na holey. chunanche jab ye tulu hoga aur log usey dekhengey to zameen par basney waley sab emaan ley aaeyngey aur ye wohi waqt hoga (jiska Sura An'aam mein zikr hai). (لا ينفع نفسا إيمانها لم تكن . ۔) ''kisi jaan ko uska emaan, agar usney us se pehley emaan na qubul kiya ho, ya emaan ke sath acchey amal na kiye huey, nafa aawar na hoga.''"
4313,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''an-qareeb dariyaaey faraat soney ka eik khazana zahir kerega, to jo wahan hazir ho us mein se kuchh na ley.''"
4314,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se usi ki misl (jaisi) riwayat kiya. magar is riwayat mein hai : ''soney ka eik pahad zahir kerega.''
4315,"Rabae bin Harash kehtey hain ke Hazrat Huzefa aur Abu-Masood (Raziallahu Anhuma) dono ikhattey huey, to Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya : main, dajjaal aur uskey sath jo kuchh hoga, us se khoob ba-khabar hun, beshak uskey sath pani ka samandar aur aag ka dariya hoga, jisey tum aag samajhtey hogey wo pani hoga aur jisey tum pani samajh rahey hogey wo aag hogi. chunanche tum mein se jo ye paey aur pani peena chahey to ussey, jisey wo aag samajhta hoga bila-shuba wo usey pani hi paeyga. Hazrat Abu-Masood badri (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : maine bhi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko aisey hi farmatey suna hai."
4316,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bayan kartey hain : ''jo bhi koi Nabi mab'oos (bheja) hua hai usney apni ummat ko kaane, jhootey dajjaal se daraya hai. khabrdar ! wo kaanaa hoga aur tumhara Rab kaanaa nahin hai, beshak dajjaal ki aakhon ke darmiyan likha hoga kafir.''"
4317,Muhammad bin Musanna ne ba-waaste Muhammad bin Jaafar Shoba se riwayat kiya ke (yun likha hoga) ''ک ف ر ''.
4318,Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se is hadees mein bayan kiya ke . . . ''usey her Muslim padh sakega.''
4319,"Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey they, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs dajjaal ke mutalliq suney to us se door rahey, Allah ki qasam ! aadmi uskey paas aaeyga jabke wo samajhta hoga ke wo sahabe-emaan hai, magar un shub'haat ki bina par jo uski taraf se uthaey jaeyngey, uski ittiba (pairwee) kar baitheyga.''"
4320,"Hazrat Ubada bin Saamit (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''bila-shuba maine tumhen dajjaal ke mutalliq (bahut kuchh) bataya hai. (iskey bawajood) mujhey andesha hai ke kahin tum ne usey na samjha ho, (yaad rakhna) Masih dajjaal thigney qad wala, bahir ko nikli tedhi pindliyon wala aur bahut ghunghraaley baalon wala hoga, eik aankh se kaanaa hoga jo ke miti hui hogi , na to ubhri hui aur na gahri hogi, phir bhi tumhen koi shubha ho to yaad rakhna ke tumhara Rab kaanaa nahin hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : Amr bin Aswad ko Qazi ka mansab (pad) saunpa gaya tha."
4321,"Hazrat Nawaas bin Samaan kilaabi (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne dajjaal ka zikr kiya aur farmaya : ''agar wo merey hotey huey tum mein zahir hua to main tumhari taraf se uska muqabla karunga. agar merey baad zahir hua to phir her shakhs khud apna difaa kerney wala hai. har musalman ke liye Shan Wala Allah hi mera khalifa hai. chunanche tum mein se jo koi usey paey to us par Sura Kahaf ki ibtidaai (shuruati) aayaat padhey yehi tumharey liye uskey fitney se aman hongi.'' ham ne puchha ke wo zameen par kitna arsa rahega? aapney farmaya : ''chaalis din. (un mein sey) eik din eik saal ke barabar aur eik din eik mahiney ke barabar aur eik din eik haftey ke barabar hoga aur baqi din tumharey dino ke barabar hongey.'' ham ne puchha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! ye din jo eik saal ke barabar hoga kya hamen us main eik din raat ki namazein kafi hongi? aapney farmaya : ''nahin, uskey liye tum log andaza laga lena.'' phir dimashq ke mashriq mein safed minaare ke paas Esa Alehissalam utrengey , isliye wo usey baab lood ke paas paeyngey aur uska kaam tamam kar dengey.''"
4322,Hazrat Abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se mazkura baala ki manind bayan kiya aur namazon ka zikr bhi usi ke ham-maani bayan kiya.
4323,"Hazrat Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aapney farmaya : ''jisney Sura Kahaf ki ibtidaai (shuruati) das aayaten hifz kar lein wo dajjaal ke fitney se mehfooz rahega . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke Hisham Dustwaai ne Qatada se isi tarah riwayat kiya hai. magar usney kaha : ''jisney Sura Kahaf ki aakhiri aayaat hifz kin. Shoba ne bhi ba-waaste Qatada ''Kahaf ki aakhiri aayaat'' ka zikr kiya hai."
4324,"Saiyedna Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''merey aur Esa Alehissalam ke darmiyan koi Nabi nahin hai, aur wo utarney waley hain, jab tum unhen dekhogey to pehchan jaogey ke darmiyani qaamat waley hain aur rang unka surkh aur safed hoga, halkey zard rang ke libas mein hongey, aisey mehsoos hoga jaisey unke sar se pani tapak raha ho, halanke nami (pani) laga nahin hoga. (intehai paakiza aur chamakdaar rang ke hongey) wo logon se Islam ke liye qitaal karengey, saleeb tod dengey aur khinzir ko qatl karengey, jiziya moquf kar dengey. Allah taala unke zamaney mein Islam ke ilawa deegar sab deeno ko khatam kar dega. wo Masih dajjaal ko halak karengey. Hazrat Esa Alehissalam zameen mein chaalis saal rahengey, phir unki wafat hogi aur musalman unka janaza padhengey.''"
4325,"Hazrat Fatima binte-Qais (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke eik raat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Isha ki Namaz mein takheer farma di. phir tashrif laye aur farmaya : ''mujhey Tameem Daari ki baaton ne rok liya tha. wo bayan kar rahey they ke samandari jazeeron mein se eik jazeerey main eik aadmi tha, aur maine eik aurat ko dekha jo apney baal khinch rahi thi. puchha ke to kon hai? usney kaha : main ''jass-saasa'' (dajjaal ko khabar karne wala janwar) hun, us mehal mein chaley jao, main wahan gaya to us main eik aadmi ko dekha jo apney baal khinch raha tha aur zanjeeron mein jakdaa hua tha aur ooper nichey uchal raha tha. maine kaha : tum kon ho? usney kaha : main dajjaal hun. kya arbon ka Nabi aa gaya hai? maine kaha : haan . usney kaha : kya un logon ne uski itaat ki hai ya nafarmani ? maine kaha : nahin balke itaat ki hai. usney kaha : ye unke liye behtar hai.''"
4326,"Hazrat Fatima binte-Qais (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki taraf se aelan kerney waley ko manadi kartey huey suna ke Namaz ke liye jama ho jao . to main bhi chali aai aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath Namaz padhi . jab aap Namaz se farigh ho gaey to member par tashrif laye aur aap hans rahey they. aapney farmaya : ''har shakhs apni jagah par baitha rahey.'' phir farmaya : ''kya jantey ho maine tumhen kyon jama kiya hai?'' unhoney kaha : Allah aur uskey Rasool behtar jantey hain. aapney farmaya : ''maine tumhen daraney ya khushkhabri sunaney ke liye jama nahin kiya hai. maine tumhen isliye jama kiya hai ke Tameem Daari esai tha, merey yahan aaya, baiat ki aur Islam qubul kiya aur usney mujhey eik baat bayan ki hai jo meri baat ki taeed mein hai jo maine tumhen dajjaal ke mutalliq kahi hai. usney mujhey bataya hai ke wo eik jahaz mein sawar hua , uskey sath qabeela lakham aur juzaam ke tees aadmi they. jahaz ko toofani mojon ne aa liya jo unhen eik mahine tak pareshan kiye rahin . . . aur wo Suraj ghuroob honey ke waqt eik jazeerey ke paas pahunchey aur eik chhoti kashti mein Sawar ho kar jazeerey mein ja utrey. to unhen eik janwar mila jiski dam bhari aur jism par bahut baal they. unhoney kaha : kambakht ! to kon hai? usney kaha : main ''jass-saasa'' (dajjaal ko khabar karne wala janwar) hun. us girjey main eik aadmi hai uskey paas jao, wo tumhari khabron ka bahut mushtaaq hai. jab usney hamarey samney aadmi ka naam liya to ham us se dar gaey ke ye kahin shaitan na ho. ham jaldi se chaley aur us girjey mein dakhil huey to eik bahut bada insan dekha, is qadr bada insan ham ne kabhi nahin dekha tha jisey badi sakhti se baandha gaya tha aur uskey haath gardan ke sath bandhey huey they. . . aur hadees bayan ki . . ۔''  usney un se (shaam ke) nakhlistan, beesaan, chashma zughar aur Nabi ummi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke mutalliq puchha . . . aur kaha ke main hi Masih (dajjaal) hun. an-qareeb mujhey nikalney ki ijazat mil jaeygi . Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''dajjaal Shaam ya Yamen ke samandar mein hai, nahin balke mashriq ki taraf mein hai.'' do baar farmaya. . . . aapney apney haath se mashriq ki taraf ishara farmaya. Sayeda Fatima binte-Qais (Raziallahu anha) kehti hain : maine ye hadees Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se yaad ki hai, aur baqiya hadees bayan ki."
4327,"Hazrat Fatima binte-Qais (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kiya ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Zohar ki Namaz padhaai phir member par tashrif laye, aur aap Jume ke alawa member par na aatey they. magar us din member par aaye . phir ye qissa bayan kiya.  Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain : ibne Sadraan Basri hain jo ibne Miswar ke sath samandar mein doob gaey they aur uskey alawa aur koi mehfooz nahin raha tha."
4328,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik roz member par khadey ho kar farmaya : ''kuchh log samandar mein ja rahey they ke unka khana khatam ho gaya , to unhen eik jazeera dikhai diya. wo roti ki talash mein usi mein chaley gaey to ''jass-saasa'' (dajjaal ko khabar karne wala janwar) se unki mulaqat ho gaee .''Waleed bin Abdullah kehtey hain ke maine Abu-Salma se puchha : ''jass-saasa'' kya hai? to usney kaha : eik aurat hai jo apney jism aur sar ke baal khinch rahi thi. usney kaha . . . us mehal mein . . . aur hadees bayan ki. aur (mehal waley aadmi ne) un se beesaan ke nakhlistan aur zaghar ke chashmey ke mutalliq maloom kiya. kaha : wohi Masih (dajjaal) hai. ibne Abu-Salma ne mujh se kaha ke is hadees main eik baat hai jo mujhey yaad nahin. kehtey hain ke Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne gawahi di ke yehi ibne Saa'id hai. maine kaha : wo to mar chuka hai. kaha agar-che (haalanki) mar gaya hai. maine kaha : usney Islam qubul kiya tha. kaha agar-che Islam qubul kiya tha. maine kaha : wo to Madiney mein bhi dakhil hua tha. kaha agar-che Madiney mein bhi dakhil hua tha."
4329,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apney chand Sahaba ke sath mein ibne Saa'id ke paas se guzrey. un Sahaba mein Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) bhi they. aur wo (ibne Saa'id Madina mein) bano maghaala ke tilon ke paas ladkon ke sath khel raha tha aur nau-umr ladka tha. usey pata na chala yahan tak ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uski kamar par apna haath maara, phir us se kaha : ''kya tu gawahi deta hai ke main Allah ka Rasool hun?'' raawi kehta hai ke ibne Saa'id ne aap ki taraf dekha, phir usney jawab diya : main gawahi deta hun ke aap ummi logon (arab) ke Rasool hain. phir ibne Sayyaad ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se kaha : kya aap gawahi detey hain ke main Allah ka Rasool hun? to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main Allah aur uskey Rasulon par emaan rakhta hun.'' phir Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usse puchha : '' terey paas kya aata hai? '' bola merey paas sachcha aata hai aur jhoota bhi. to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' tujh par maamla khalt-malt kar diya gaya hai.'' phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''maine terey liye eik baat chupai hai.'' jabke aapney apney dil mein ye aayat khayal farmaee thi : (يوم تأتي السماء بدخان مبين) ibne Sayyaad ne kaha : wo (''الدخ'') hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''dafa ho, to apni qadr se hergiz aagey nahin badh sakta.''  to Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! mujhey ijazat den mein iski gardan maar dun, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar ye wohi hua to tum is par hergiz musallat nahin ho saktey. yani dajjaal . . . aur agar ye wo nahin hai to phir iskey qatl mein khair nahin.''"
4330,Saiyedna ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) kaha kartey they : Allah ki qasam ! mujhey is mein koi shak nahin ke Masih dajjaal (yehi) ibne-Sayyad hi hai.
4331,Muhammad bin Mankadr kehtey hain ke maine Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) ko dekha ke wo Allah ki qasam utha kar kehtey they ke ibne Sayyaad hi dajjaal hai. maine kaha : aap Allah ki qasam utha kar kehtey hain? unhoney kaha : maine Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) se suna ke wo is baat par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke samney qasam uthatey they magar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne is par inkar nahin farmaya.
4332,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke ham ne Harra waley din ibne Sayyaad ko gum paya.
4333,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''us waqt tak qiyamat nahin aaeygi jab tak ke tees (intehai jhootey) dajjaal na aa jaeyn, her eik ka daawa hoga ke wo Allah ka Rasool hai.''"
4334,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''us waqt tak qiyamat nahin aaeygi jab tak ke tees intehai jhootey faraibi (dajjaal) na aa jaeyn . un mein se her eik Allah aur uskey Rasool par jhoot boltaa hoga.''"
4335,Ubaida Salmaani ne ye riwayat bayan ki aur mazkura baala hadees ki manind riwayat kiya. Ibrahim bin Yazid Nakhai kehtey hain ke maine Ubeda se kaha : kya bhala aap Mukhtaar (bin Abi Ubaid Saqafi) ko unhi mein se samajhtey hain? unhoney kaha : ye to un sab ke sardaron mein se hai.
4336,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''pehla-pehla nuqs aur aeb jo bani-Israel mein dakhil hua ye tha ke un mein se koi doosrey se milta to usey kehta tha : arey ! Allah se daro aur jo kar rahey ho us se baaz aa jao, ye tumharey liye halal nahin. phir agley din milta to uskey liye uska ham-niwala, ham piyala aur ham majlis honey mein usey koi rukawat na hoti thi. jab unka ye haal ho gaya tu Allah taala ne unke dilon ko eik doosrey par dey maara (unke andar ikhtilaf, tanaaza' (jhagdaa) aur bughz aur hasad paida ho gaya. un mein se ittifaq aur ittihaad aur ulfat utha li gaee) phir aapney ye aayat padhi (لعن الذين كفروا من بني إسرائيل . ۔) ''bani Israel ke kafiron par Hazrat Dawud aur Esa ibne Maryam ki zabani lanat ki gaee us wajeh se ke wo nafarmaniyan kartey they aur had se aagey badh jatey they. aapas main eik doosrey ko burey kamon se jo wo kartey they, roktey na they. jo kuchh bhi wo kartey they yaqinan bahut bura tha. un mein se aksar ko aap dekhengey ke wo kafiron se dostiyaan kartey hain, bahut bura hai wo jo unhoney apney liye aagey bhej rakha hai ke Allah un se naraz hua aur wo hamesha azab mein rahengey. agar unka Allah par, Nabi par aur us par jo uski taraf nazil kiya gaya, emaan hota to ye un kafiron se dostiyaan na rakhtey lekin aksar un mein se fasiq hain.'' phir farmaya : ''khabrdar ! Allah ki qasam ! tumhen bil-zaroor neki ka hukm karna hoga , burai se rokna hoga , zalim ka haath pakadna hoga aur usey haq par lautaanaa aur haq ka paband karna hoga .''"
4337,"Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se is hadees ki manind riwayat kiya. aur mazeed kaha . . . : ''warna Allah taala tumharey dil eik doosrey par dey maarey ga (tumharey andar ikhtilaf aur tafarqa (bhed) dal dega) aur phir usi tarah lanat kerega jaisey ke unko lanat ki thi.'' (apni rehmat se door kerega.) Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : is riwayat ko Mahaaribi ne ba-sand Ala bin Musaiyab , Abdullah bin Amr bin Murra sey, unhoney Salim Iftus sey, unhoney Abu-Ubaida sey, unhoney Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se. aur Khalid Taahaan ne ba-waaste Ala , Amr bin Murra se aur usney Abu-Ubaida se riwayat kiya."
4338,"Janab Qais (bin Abi Hazim ( ne bayan kiya ke Hazrat Abu-Bakar Siddiq (Raziallahu anhu) ne (apney khutbey mein) Shan Wale Allah ki hamd aur sanaa ke baad farmaya : ''aey logo ! tum ye aayat kareema padhtey to ho : (عليكم أنفسكم لا يضركم . ۔) ''aey emaan walo ! apni fikr karo, jab tum raah-raast par chal rahey ho to jo shakhs gumrah ho us se tumhara koi nuqsan nahin.'' magar uskey maani aur mafhoom ghalat samajhtey ho. Khalid ne riwayat kiya. . . ham ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna hai : ''bila-shuba log jab kisi ko zulm karta dekhen aur phir uskey haath na pakdein to qarib hota hai ke Allah un sab ko azab ke lapet mein le-ley.'' aur Amr (bin Aun ( ne Hasheem se riwayat kartey huey kaha : halanke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna hai : ''jis qom mein Allah ki nafarmani ke kaam hon aur wo unhen rokney par qadir hon magar mana na kartey hon to qarib hota hai ke Allah us sabab se un sab ko apney azaab ki lapet mein le-ley. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : is riwayat ko . . . isi tarah jaisey ke Khalid ne . . . riwayat kiya hai. Abu-Usama aur eik badi jamaat ne bayan kiya hai. jabke Shoba ne yun bayan kiya : ''jis kisi qom mein nafarmaniyan hoti hon aur muaasi (gunaah) se bachney walon ki tadaad ziyada . . . aur doosron ki kam ho. . . (aur phir bhi wo na ruken to un sab par azaab aaney ka andesha hota hai.'')"
4339,"Hazrat Jarir bin Abdullah Bijli (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : ''jo koi aisi qom mein ho ke un mein Allah ki nafarmaniyan ki ja rahi hon aur wo log unki islah aur unke badalney par qadir hon, iskey bawajood wo unki islah na keren aur unhen na badlein tu Allah taala un sab ko unke marney se pehley azab dega.''"
4340,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, wo kehtey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : ''tum mein se jo koi kisi burai ko dekhay aur wo usey apney haath se badal deney aur uski islah ki taqat rakhta ho to usey chahiye ke haath se uski islah (sudhaar) karey'' . . . Hannaad ne ye hadees yahin tak bayan ki . jabkey ibne Ala ne baqiya ko yun pura kiya. . . ''agar ye himmat na ho to zaban se rokey , agar zaban se rokney ki himmat na ho to phir apney dil se bura janey aur ye emaan ki sab se kamzor kaifiyat hai.''"
4341,"abu-Umaiya Sha'baani kehtey hain ke maine Hazrat Abu-Solba Khushni (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha : aey Abu-Solba ! aap us aayate-karima ( عليكم أنفسكم . . . الخ (ke silsiley mein kya kehtey hain? unhoney kaha : Allah ki qasam ! tum ne uskey mutalliq haqeeqat mein sahibe-ilm w khabar se puchha hai. maine uskey mutalliq Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se puchha tha, to aapney farmaya tha : '' balke tumhen chahiye ke neki ka hukm diye jao aur burai se roktey raho yahan tak ke jab dekho ke hirs aur bakheeli ki ittiba honey lagi hai, log khaahishate-nafsani ke dar pai ho gaey hain aur duniya hi ko tarjeeh deney lagey hain (aakhirat ko bhool gaey hain (aur her raey wala apni raey aur baat hi ko tarjeeh deta hai. (us par khush aur israr karta hai) to phir apney aap ko lazim pakad lo aur Awam ki fikr chhod do ( doosron ki gumrahi tumhen nuqsan nahin degi .) bila-shuba tumharey baad sabr ke din aaney waley hain, un mein) deen w shariyat par) sabr karna (us par Sabit qadam rehna ( aisey hoga jaisey aag ka angaara pakadna. un logon mein (deen ke taqaazon par) amal kerney waley ko us jaisey pachas aamilon ka sawab milega .'' ( Abdullah bin Mubarak ne kaha ke Utba ke ilawa ( mujhey doosrey ne bataya ke Hazrat Abu-Solba (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! un logon mein se pachas aamilon ke barabar sawab milega ? aapney farmaya : '' tumharey pachas aamilon ke barabar .''"
4342,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' tumhara us zamaney mein kya haal hoga. . . '' ya farmaya : '' an-qareeb aisa zamana aaney wala hai ke logon ko khoob chhan liya jaeyga ( ahle-eman aur achey aadmi utha liye jaeyngey (aur chhan bura baqi reh jaeyga (be-deen aur neech log baqi reh jaeyngey ( jinkey waadon mein be wafai aur amanaton mein khayanat hogi aur un mein is tarah se ikhtilaf ho jaeyga . . . '' aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney haathon ki ungliyon ko eik dusri ke andar dal kar dikhaya . . . Sahaba ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! to ham kya keren? aapney farmaya : ''jo neki ho us par amal paira hona aur jo burai ho us se door rehna aur khas apni islah ki fikr karna aur apney aam logon ko chhod dena . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : ye riwayat Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu Anhuma) ke wastey se Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se kaee sanadon se waarid hai."
4343,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke eik dafa ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke ird-gird bethey huey they ke aapney fitnon ka zikr kya. aapney farmaya : ''jab tum dekho ke log apney ehad w mawaaeed mein be wafai kerney lagey hain, amanaton ka maamla intehai khafeef aur kamzor ho gaya hai) log khaain ban gaey hain (aur unki aapas ki haalat is tarah ho gaee hai.'' aur aapney apni ungliyon ko eik doosrey ke andar dal kar dikhaya ( ikhtilafat bahut badh gaey hain ( Abdullah kehtey hain ke main uth kar aap ke qarib ho gaya aur arz kya : Allah mujhey aap par fida honey wala banaey ! main un halaat mein kya karun ? aapney farmaya : '' apney ghar ko lazim pakadna , apni zaban ka Malik bin jana ( khamosh rehna (aur neki par amal karna aur burai se bachna aur apni zaat ki fikr karna aur aam logon ki fikr chhod dena .''"
4344,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' sab se afzal jihad ye hai ke insan Jabir haakim ya zalim ameer ke samney haq w insaf ka kalma keh guzrey .''"
4345,"Janab Urs bin umaira Kandi (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab zameen mein koi khata aur nafarmani ki jaey to us mein hazir aur mojud shakhs ne usko bura jana . . . aur eik baar farmaya. . . aur uska inkar kya. . . to wo aisey hoga jaisey us gunaah aur nafarmani se ghayeb aur door raha lekin jo ghayeb aur door tha magar us nafarmani ko usney pasand kya to wo aisey hoga jaisey ke us mein hazir aur mojud tha.''"
4346,Hazrat Adi bin Adi (Rahimahullah) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se mazkura baala hadees ki manind riwayat kya. kaha : ''jo us mein hazir tha magar usney usey makruh aur napasand jana to wo aisey hua jaisey ke us se ghayeb aur door raha ho.''
4347,"Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke Sahaba kiram mein se eik sahabi ne bayan kya, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' log us waqt tak hergiz halak nahin hongey jab tak ke unke gunahon aur uyoob ki kasrat na ho jaey ya unka koi uzr baqi na rahey .''"
4348,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai, wo kehtey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney aakhiri dinon mein hamen eik din Isha ki Namaz padhaai . jab salam phera to khadey ho gaey aur farmaya : '' dekho ke tumhari is raat mein ab jo koi poori zameen par mojud hai so saal ke baad un mein se koi baqi nahin rahega .'' Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) kehtey hain ke log Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke us farman ke baarey mein weham mein pad gaey hain. . . yani ye ahadis jo Sahaba kiram so saal ke baarey mein riwayat kartey hain (ke shayad so saal baad qiyamat hi aa jaeygi unhoney kaha ( halanke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne to sirf ye farmaya tha ke aaj jo roey zameen par mojud hai, wo baqi nahin rahega . maqsad ye tha ke ye sadi khatam ho jaeygi ."
4349,"Hazrat Abu-Solba Khushni (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah taala is ummat ko aadhey din ki mohlat se aajiz nahin rakhega .''"
4350,"Hazrat Saad bin abi Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mujhey umeed hai ke meri ummat apney rab ke yahan is baat se aajiz na hogi ke wo usey aadhey din tak muakhkhar farma dey .'' Hazrat Saad (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha gaya ke aadhey din ki muddat kis qadr hai? unhoney kaha : paanch so saal ."
